Turkish Central Bank Against Further Decline in Lira, Basci Says

-- B y   M a r k   B e n t l e y
-- 
2011-09-30T08:16:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/turkish-central-bank-against-further-decline-in-lira-basci-says.html
Turkish central bank governor Erdem Basci said he wouldn’t welcome further losses for the lira.  The decline in the lira has been “useful and sufficient,”
Basci said in a speech in the northwestern city of Edirne today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mark Bentley at 
 mbentley3@bloomberg.net  